title: Total Canadian vehicles returning to the country in Canada 2021
summary: The graph shows the trend of the Total Number of Canadian vehicles returning to Canada during the year 2021 .
The Number drops between January and February shows the minimum value in February .
From February on it increases and shows the maximum value in August .
gold: This graph shows the total Canadian vehicles returning to the country in 2021 , each month . The graph has a general upward trend . It was at its lowest point in Feb and its highest point in Dec .
